      \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_0\"\u003e\n\n                    \u003ch3\u003eSummary\u003c/h3\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e    \u003cul\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Samsung debuts a folding gaming handheld at MWC 2025.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        The device is a proof-of-concept prototype with a 7.2-inch foldable display.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        There\u0026#39;s uncertainty on whether Samsung will release it (or anything similar) as a market-ready product.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMobile World Congress 2025 is in full swing. There\u0026#39;s a glut of newly announced AI novelties, like \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/live-video-screen-sharing-coming-to-gemini-live-this-month/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGemini Live video and screen-sharing\u003c/a\u003e, and one hardware reveal that stands out from the many awesome global smartphones we\u0026#39;re getting first looks at. That reveal is of the Samsung Flex Gaming, the folding handheld that\u0026#39;s been in the works for quite some time (Source: \u003ca href=\"https://global.samsungdisplay.com/31346\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSamsung Display\u003c/a\u003e via \u003ca href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Flex-Gaming-Samsung-showcases-unusual-foldable-gaming-handheld-running-high-end-PC-game.971547.0.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNotebookcheck\u003c/a\u003e). Among the many things we have yet to learn is if this theoretical handheld would aim for the bug guns like the ROG Ally X, or the selection of \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-android-gaming-handhelds/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eless-costly Android handheld consoles\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"one-defining-feature-sets-it-apart\"\u003e\n            One defining feature sets it apart\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;The crease on the Samsung Galaxy Z Flip 6 (left) next to the Galaxy Z Flip 4 (right).\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Galaxy Z Flip 6 vs Z Flip 4 crease comparisons\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/galaxy-z-flip-6-vs-z-flip-4-ap-18.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eThe crease on the Samsung Galaxy Z Flip 6 (left) next to the Galaxy Z Flip 4 (right).\u003c/p\u003e\n                        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNo word yet on if it has a visible crease.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eSamsung\u0026#39;s promise to increase innovation came after the S25 lineup was mostly set in stone. To the South Korean tech giant\u0026#39;s credit, the S25 Slim came basically out of nowhere, with a thin form factor that\u0026#39;s a big enough deal for \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/rumor-samsung-galaxy-s25-slim-vs-apple-iphone-17-slim-late-2025/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eApple to also go skinny\u003c/a\u003e with the iPhone 17 Air.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe Flex Gaming handheld, on the other hand, has hidden just under the surface for months. Nearly half a year ago, we caught wind of Valve\u0026#39;s work \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/valve-testing-arm64-support-could-bring-steam-games-to-smartphones/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eporting Steam games to ARM64 platforms\u003c/a\u003e. Three months later, a clever Android Police investigator compiled \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/a-foldable-samsung-gaming-handheld-multiple-rumors/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efour separate leaks\u003c/a\u003e indicating Samsung\u0026#39;s folding console was all but a certainty.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"2d0b-4b49-bb21cca0a838\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/gaming-brands-should-make-a-handheld-list/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"An Android game handheld on a purple background\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/gaming-handheld-1.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eNow, it\u0026#39;s here. Or, more accurately, it\u0026#39;s in Barcelona, at MWC 2025, installed next to a host of other devices touting Samsung Display\u0026#39;s tireless work to perfect the OLED screen and its various applications. That\u0026#39;s actually the rub with the folding console: The Flex Gaming, like the other Samsung tech immediately surrounding it, bears the \u0026#34;concept\u0026#34; title, meaning it\u0026#39;s not an official device that\u0026#39;s ready to hit the market. Yet.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"what-we-know-about-the-samsung-flex-gaming\"\u003e\n                        What we know about the Samsung Flex Gaming\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 id=\"not-much-so-far-because-it-39-s-only-a-model\"\u003e\n            Not much so far, because it\u0026#39;s only a model\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\n\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                                                        \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source: Samsung\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2500\" height=\"1708\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"An installation of Samsung Display prototypes at MWC 2025.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/samsung-display-concepts-mwc-2025.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eSource: Samsung\u003c/p\u003e\n                        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eThe Flex Gaming and other featured Samsung Display technologies at MWC 2025.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWe know the device we\u0026#39;re looking at here has a 7.2-inch display that folds in half. Its joysticks fit neatly in opposing indentations created just for that purpose. We also weren\u0026#39;t allowed to touch it, and it doesn\u0026#39;t have any buttons or a D-pad — wait, what?\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAt the moment, the Flex Gaming is more a proof-of-concept prototype than anything resembling a real attempt at a pocket-size SteamOS console. To be more direct, there\u0026#39;s zero indication we\u0026#39;ll ever see this thing in real life. If we do, it\u0026#39;ll look different out of necessity, because not many games work great with just two thumbsticks. And when a folding console does hit the market, it might be from a totally different company that simply buys Samsung Display\u0026#39;s folding OLED.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"221a-4602-b5b6b4b88d7c\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/features-xbox-gaming-handheld-list/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Mashed up concept of Xbox gaming handheld with Lenovo Legion Go\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/xboxhandhelkd.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSo, while our tireless reporting fell a bit flat in the \u0026#34;real-world devices\u0026#34; sense this time around — although it was \u003cem\u003etechnically\u003c/em\u003e correct — there is still hope. Samsung may or may not have the ambition to combine its various in-house endeavors (from the branches responsible for Exynos chips or GDDR6 volatile memory, for example), but the hardest part to manufacture is apparently almost ready for primetime. Much like the \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/first-look-google-samsung-android-xr-headset/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAndroid XR collaboration with Google\u003c/a\u003e, the Flex Gaming is more evidence that Samsung has its hands in a number of today\u0026#39;s fastest-moving electronics categories.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
